{"tid":420004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係唔明 一名打工仔可以買成萬幾蚊一件野去裝飾自己","createTime":"2017-10-01T04:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T04:48:28.000Z","uid":62424,"like":498,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"0d62f569075ae428f4294e543309a77fcf2f2a7a","tid":420004,"uid":62424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:34:11.000Z","msg":"例如萬幾蚊去買對鞋 幾千蚊去買件衫 褲等等<br />\n我真係唔明佢地係咩心態 咁當然你係有錢仔既話緊係無問題啦。<br />\n但我明明見到好多都只係一名普通既打工仔 就花大量錢去買一件炒到好貴既潮流野 究竟係咩心態？<br />\n型？一句好現實既說話 你個樣柒 著到幾貴都無用啦<br />\n去炫耀？但事實你係窮撚喎 外面睇落去有錢 內面窮到系咁"},{"pid":"ab75f606044d7c4c7f5bf872e46ee92a8ba0a5b7","tid":420004,"uid":65530,"like":14,"dislike":121,"score":-107,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:35:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"038597501ed7c127d7571f9da322e8f231c266a9","tid":420004,"uid":146031,"like":6,"dislike":37,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左手袋同首飾名牌係ok<br />\n<br />\n其他買名牌都唔抵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n手袋都不了<br />\n<br />\n只有鑽石 金器 手錶"},{"pid":"c14bad1b0b1ee6035b10ac39166b01715c584bb4","tid":420004,"uid":62424,"like":7,"dislike":15,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:41:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>除左手袋同首飾名牌係ok<br />\n<br />\n其他買名牌都唔抵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n手袋都不了<br />\n<br />\n只有鑽石 金器 手錶</blockquote><br />\n同意 起碼保值先"},{"pid":"f75be2f459e21c9c857d18fb0f23d2cfc255e25b","tid":420004,"uid":293,"like":124,"dislike":2,"score":122,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除左手袋同首飾名牌係ok<br />\n<br />\n其他買名牌都唔抵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n手袋都不了<br />\n<br />\n只有鑽石 金器 手錶</blockquote><br />\n同意 起碼保值先</blockquote><br />\n鑽石保值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21139fbfaca785b0e08981cab6ff222bf3ae30ac","tid":420004,"uid":48743,"like":116,"dislike":14,"score":102,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:51:07.000Z","msg":"系你老母，你理撚得人？"},{"pid":"e44e7ec7d6c08b4a3fb96a25f71927a4e8e2389a","tid":420004,"